name: What's wrong with my car?!
description:
What's wrong with my car?! is a simple driving game where you need to survive as long as you can driving a chaotic shapeshifting car.

If you crash against a wall or run out of fuel you lose.

This game will likely be updated some time in the near future with different maps and extra cars!

This game was made during the Mini Jam 74: Chaos.
